tspan.tspan: This button creates a new note in a seperate window. This way,
you can have multiple notes on your desktop!
This is the button that saves your work.You can either use this
button,or the keyboard shortcut Ctrl + S. You only need to do this
the first time, because of the Autosave feature.
If you have a link selected,you can click this button to open this
link in the browser.This only works if you have tagged your text as
a link in the bottom bar (See 12)
